Title : Taleomy Indian Reserve No. 3
Text : '''Taleomy Indian Reserve No. 3''', officially '''Taleomy 3''', is an [[Indian reserve]] under the governance of the [[Nuxalk Nation]], located at the mouth of the [[Taleomey River]]<ref>[http://apps.gov.bc.ca/pub/bcgnws/names/64994.html BC Names/GeoBC "Taleomy 3 (Indian reserve)"]</ref> on the east shore of [[South Bentinck Arm]] in the [[British Columbia Coast|Central Coast region]] of [[British Columbia]], [[Canada]].

